snippet.title: Trap Tower Trials - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Trap Tower Trials is a 3D single-player platformer that will test your dexterity with various traps and obstacles. This game is designed to be a challenge; therefore, we are not responsible for any peripherals broken in anger. Do you think you'll be able to climb the tower?

Want to try the demo version ? https://store.steampowered.com/app/2728340/Trap_Tower_Trials/
Don't forget to wishlist the game on Steam !
